    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                    <h1 class="h3 mb-0"><i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> About Job Tracker</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4>What is Job Tracker?</h4>
                    <p>
                        Job Tracker is a comprehensive job search management application that helps you organize, track, 
                        and analyze your job applications across multiple job boards. With browser extensions for major 
                        job sites and powerful filtering capabilities, you can streamline your entire job search process.
                    </p>

                    <h4>Core Features</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Multi-Platform Support</strong> - Browser extensions for LinkedIn, Indeed, S1Jobs, Welcome to the Jungle, and EnergyJobSearch</li>
                        <li><strong>Automatic Job Extraction</strong> - Capture job listings with one click from supported job sites</li>
                        <li><strong>Smart Rules Engine</strong> - Automatically classify jobs based on custom rules you define</li>
                        <li><strong>Application Tracking</strong> - Monitor your application status through multiple stages (Applied, Pending, Interview, Offer, etc.)</li>
                        <li><strong>Interest & Suitability Ratings</strong> - Mark jobs by interest level and suitability to focus on the best opportunities</li>
                        <li><strong>Advanced Filtering & Search</strong> - Filter by title, company, location, salary, remote status, and more</li>
                        <li><strong>Job Description Auto-Fetch</strong> - Automatically capture full job descriptions when you visit job pages</li>
                         <li><strong>Contacts</strong> - Track recruiters/hiring managers and log interactions per job or globally</li>
                        <li><strong>Activity History</strong> - Complete audit trail of all changes and actions on your job listings</li>
                        <li><strong>Manual Entry Support</strong> - Add jobs manually for sites without extensions</li>
                        <li><strong>Crawl Pages</strong> - Maintain a list of additional search/listing pages to crawl, with per-page delays and optional <code>{n}</code> URL substitution ranges</li>
                        <li><strong>Skills Tracking</strong> - Track required skills across different job listings</li>
                        <li><strong>WhatsApp Sharing</strong> - Quickly share job opportunities via WhatsApp</li>
                        <li><strong>Multi-User Support</strong> - Secure authentication with separate data for each user</li>
                    </ul>

